<title>USA: Raychem board approves $300 mln for buyback.</title>
<headline>Raychem board approves $300 mln for buyback.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif 1997-07-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Raychem Corp said its board authorized management to repurchase up to $300 million of common stock during any fiscal year to offset the dilutive effects of the company's stock purchase and stock option plans.</p>
<p>The new authorization will take effect in fiscal 1998.</p>
</text>
